  "imageCount": 5,
  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/3523a4d5ccacb241.jpg?v=1782534355\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Kicking off 2017 with my newest collection with American Crafts, On A Whim! It was definitely inspired by the optimistic and confident girls and women out their doing fun things and seeking bright and bold adventures. I can't wait to see how you document your life with this mix of color and whimsy.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/4c55c096cf586c30.jpg?v=1782534358\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Capture spontaneity and fun times with On a Whim. Bold graphics and cool patterns complement fun phrases in a host of bright colors. Pineapple yellow, flamingo pink and ocean blue coordinate with accents of gold, green, and red. Document your favorite adventures with the cute icons of On a Whim!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"1c-_AC_AT_OnAWhim_CreativeSamples-4.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/ae8886bebf5a9761.jpg?v=1782534361\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"1d-AT_OnAWhim_Blog_Images-01.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/d1d7c7e349c9942c.jpg?v=1782534364\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"1e-AT_OnAWhim_Blog_Images-02.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/87ed44b59de09834.jpg?v=1782534367\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Let us know what your favorites are in the comments! I'll be at <a href=\"http://www.creativationshow.org/\">Creativation</a> (formerly CHA) in a couple weeks in Phoenix, AZ and I'll be sure to capture and share it with you here and on my <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/amytangerine1\">YouTube channel</a>.</p>"
}